    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It offers a smooth ride and remains a very dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
