      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with minor cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows some age with moderate clear coat peeling on the roof and a few small door dings, while the interior has some visible wear on the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 19500.0,
